description:
Below Deck - Season 1, Episode 10




Reunion Special

Hosted by Bravo's Andy Cohen, the reunion brings Adrienne Gang, Aleks Taldykin, Ben Robinson, C.J. Lebeau, David Bradberry, Eddie Lucas, Kat Held, and Sam Orme to discuss some of the most talked about antics of the first season. Captain Lee also joins the crew to give his perspective on this season's charters.




Original Air Date: 02-Sep-2013
